1. create a function like mentioned in utils. js
2. install mocha js in npm using npm i mocha --save-dev
3. create test case like the on in utils.test.js
4. change the package json "test": "mocha **/*.test.js"
5. use npm test

note:
nodemon --exec 'npm test'(linux/mac)
nodemon --exec "npm test"(windows) 
to auto restart test case